@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ldjpmy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v1 / wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.03)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v2 + 0.08 - v0 + 0.38)))
    v0 = (v1 * ((tmp + 0.82 * v2 + 0.16) * (tmp + 0.69 * v0 + 0.14)))
    v0 = (v1 / 0.42)
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = 0.93
    data[tid] = v0
